00:50:36.266 --> 00:50:46.187
or maybe 170 tokens. And so, in LLMER, we pass other types of input with content underscore

00:50:46.187 --> 00:50:53.386
functions. So, for images, we use content image file. This passes an image from your local file

00:50:53.386 --> 00:51:00.907
system to the chat. You can also do the same thing if you have an image at a particular URL

00:51:00.907 --> 00:51:07.227
with content image URL. Or if you have a PDF, you want to extract information from that PDF

00:51:07.227 --> 00:51:16.586
