00:53:34.266 --> 00:53:41.067
use type object to make a list. This is going to specify that we need a list. And then name should

00:53:41.067 --> 00:53:45.467
be a string and age should be an integer. There are type functions for all the types.

00:53:46.907 --> 00:53:52.347
